videoSnippet.title: Bobby Fischer Praised Tigran Petrosian for His Queen Sacrifice
videoSnippet.description:
You are awesome - Have an excellent day! :)

Tigran V Petrosian vs Ludek Pachman
"A Real Problem Move" (game of the day Feb-26-2002)
Bled (1961), Bled YUG, rd 6, Sep-10
Formation: King's Indian Attack (A07)

1. Nf3 c5 2. g3 Nc6 3. Bg2 g6 4. O-O Bg7 5. d3 e6 6. e4 Nge7 7. Re1 O-O 8. e5 d6 9. ed6 Qd6 10. Nbd2 Qc7 11. Nb3 Nd4 12. Bf4 Qb6 13. Ne5 Nb3 14. Nc4 Very nice tempo move. --Fischer 14... Qb5 15. ab3 a5 16. Bd6 Bf6 17. Qf3 Kg7 18. Re4 Now Petrosian is preparing for a very beautiful finish.--Fischer 18... Rd8 19. Qf6 Kf6 20. Be5 Kg5 21. Bg7 This is a real problem move. --Fischer
